CREATE TABLE customers AS SELECT * FROM customers LIMIT 0

SELECT c.customer_name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) as total_expenditure FROM customers c JOIN orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY c.customer_id ORDER BY total_expenditure DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) as total_expenditure FROM customers c JOIN orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY c.customer_id ORDER BY total_expenditure DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.list_price * (1 - oi.discount)) as total_expenditure FROM customers c JOIN orders o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY c.customer_id ORDER BY total_expenditure DESC LIMIT 5
